‘‘Channaṃ , bhikkhave, pātubhāvo dullabho lokasmiṃ. Katamesaṃ channaṃ? Tathāgatassa arahato sammāsambuddhassa pātubhāvo dullabho lokasmiṃ, tathāgatappaveditassa dhammavinayassa desetā puggalo dullabho lokasmiṃ, ariyāyatane paccājāti dullabhā 
