	Alternative{lang='vri', text='paccājāti dullabhā'}
	Alternative{lang='syā.', text='paccājāto dullabho'}}
lokasmiṃ, indriyānaṃ avekallatā dullabhā lokasmiṃ, ajaḷatā aneḷamūgatā dullabhā lokasmiṃ, kusale dhamme chando 
Note { id=1, line='12', referenceLine='3', original='kusaladhammacchando (sī. syā. pī.)', type='auto', previous=' lokasmiṃ, indriyānaṃ avekallatā dullabhā lokasmiṃ, ajaḷatā aneḷamūgatā dullabhā lokasmiṃ, kusale dhamme chando '
