dullabho lokasmiṃ. Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, channaṃ pātubhāvo dullabho lokasmi’’nti. Paṭhamaṃ.

‘‘Chayime, bhikkhave, ānisaṃsā sotāpattiphalasacchikiriyāya. Katame cha? Saddhammaniyato hoti, aparihānadhammo hoti, pariyantakatassa dukkhaṃ hoti 
Note { id=2, line='21', referenceLine='5', original='dukkhaṃ na hoti (syā. pī. ka.)', type='auto', previous=' Chayime, bhikkhave, ānisaṃsā sotāpattiphalasacchikiriyāya. Katame cha? Saddhammaniyato hoti, aparihānadhammo hoti, pariyantakatassa dukkhaṃ hoti '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='dukkhaṃ hoti'}
	Alternative{lang='syā. pī. ka.', text='dukkhaṃ na hoti'}}
, asādhāraṇena ñāṇena samannāgato hoti, hetu cassa sudiṭṭho, hetusamuppannā ca dhammā. Ime kho, bhikkhave, cha ānisaṃsā sotāpattiphalasacchikiriyāyā’’ti. Dutiyaṃ.

 ‘‘‘So vata, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kañci saṅkhāraṃ niccato samanupassanto anulomikāya khantiyā samannāgato bhavissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. ‘Anulomikāya khantiyā asamannāgato sammattaniyāmaṃ okkamissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. ‘Sammattaniyāmaṃ anokkamamāno sotāpattiphalaṃ vā sakadāgāmiphalaṃ vā anāgāmiphalaṃ vā arahattaṃarahattaphalaṃ 
Note { id=3, line='30', referenceLine='7', original='arahattaphalaṃ (ka.) paṭi. ma. 3.36', type='auto', previous=' ‘So vata, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kañci saṅkhāraṃ niccato samanupassanto anulomikāya khantiyā samannāgato bhavissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. ‘Anulomikāya khantiyā asamannāgato sammattaniyāmaṃ okkamissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. ‘Sammattaniyāmaṃ anokkamamāno sotāpattiphalaṃ vā sakadāgāmiphalaṃ vā anāgāmiphalaṃ vā arahattaṃ '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='arahattaṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='arahattaphalaṃ'}}
vā sacchikarissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati.

‘‘‘So  vata, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabbasaṅkhāresabbasaṅkhāraṃ 
