‘‘Cha , bhikkhave, ānisaṃse sampassamānena alameva bhikkhunā sabbasaṅkhāresu anodhiṃ karitvā aniccasaññaṃ upaṭṭhāpetuṃ. Katame cha? ‘Sabbasaṅkhārā ca me anavatthitāanavaṭṭhitato 
