	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='na ramissati'}}
, sabbalokā ca me mano vuṭṭhahissati, nibbānapoṇañca me mānasaṃ bhavissati, saṃyojanā ca me pahānaṃ gacchissantigacchanti 
